VS-CODE Pluggins:
ES Lint
Material Icon Theme
Path Intellisense -> better for import
Prettier - Code formator

=======
tsc app.ts --> it will generate app.js javascript file

=======
npm init --> It will create Package.json file
=== ==
Create node_modules
npm install --save-dev lite-server
Then in your script add:
"start": "lite-server"

- lite-server is simple development server. It looks index.htm near to package.json
  ==
  npm start
  It will run local host - http://localhost:3000/
